15:49.164 --> 15:50.541
Who the hell are you?!

15:50.565 --> 15:52.209
- No, no, no, no, no!
- Hey, hey, hey!

15:52.233 --> 15:53.277
- Hey!
- Roller!

15:53.301 --> 15:54.812
Hey! What are you doing?!

15:54.836 --> 15:56.681
♪ ...get you one

16:02.043 --> 16:03.954
D, I got to go! God!

16:03.978 --> 16:05.444
Shit!

16:05.446 --> 16:06.824
Hello?!

16:06.848 --> 16:08.159
Shit.

16:28.403 --> 16:30.848
Get down. Get down!

16:34.409 --> 16:35.986
Shit!

16:41.216 --> 16:43.383
Front door open.

16:47.889 --> 16:49.133
Dean!

16:49.157 --> 16:51.068
What are you doing?

16:51.092 --> 16:52.737
I'm... I'm going to the crime scene

16:52.761 --> 16:54.493
