16:56.231 --> 16:57.408
With my gun?!

16:57.432 --> 16:59.343
Are you... Have you lost your mind?

16:59.367 --> 17:00.878
My... My Lyft will be here
in two minutes.

17:00.902 --> 17:02.213
- Two.
- Give me the gun.

17:02.237 --> 17:03.814
