17:03.838 --> 17:05.704
then how am I gonna kill
the shooter when I locate him?

17:05.705 --> 17:09.420
Dean, take your black ass
back in the house... now!

17:09.444 --> 17:10.459
No.

17:10.483 --> 17:11.821
Gilbert and his Kia Sorento

17:11.846 --> 17:13.624
will be here any moment, Des.

17:13.647 --> 17:15.560
Boy, I don't give a shit if you waiting

17:15.584 --> 17:17.516
for George Clinton and the Mothership.

17:17.518 --> 17:19.829
- I am not playing with you, Dean Simms.
- Dessy, I'm a man!

17:19.854 --> 17:21.698
And a man is supposed
to take care of his lady.

17:21.722 --> 17:22.900
He's supposed to protect her.

17:22.924 --> 17:24.435
He's supposed to protect his lady.

17:24.861 --> 17:27.726
Dean, you are a black man with a gun.

17:27.728 --> 17:30.241
- Remember Philando Castile?
- Yes, Des.

17:30.265 --> 17:32.109
- Remember that?
- Yes, yes, yes, Des, yes.

17:32.133 --> 17:33.532
Dean, I...

17:33.534 --> 17:38.405
I am tired of taking care
of everything and everybody.

17:41.810 --> 17:45.056
- Somebody tried to kill me. Hmm?
- Mm.

17:45.080 --> 17:46.857
- And you just killed somebody.
- Mm.

17:46.881 --> 17:48.659
And now you want to
go out in these streets

17:48.683 --> 17:50.261
and hurt somebody else?

17:50.285 --> 17:52.151
I'm not having it.

17:52.153 --> 17:54.331
Gimme the goddamn gun! Now!

17:54.355 --> 17:56.533
Okay, okay, fine.

17:56.557 --> 17:57.735
Take it.

17:57.759 --> 18:00.271
It was forcefully stated.
I'll stay for now.

18:00.295 --> 18:01.939
But... But I'm gonna find out who did it,

18:01.963 --> 18:04.074
and... and then I'm gonna kill him.

18:13.851 --> 18:15.791
I want you to go sit down in the chapel

18:15.815 --> 18:17.653
where it's nice and quiet
for a little bit, okay?

18:17.655 --> 18:19.551
- Yeah, okay.
- Okay.

18:19.575 --> 18:21.091
Hey.

18:21.115 --> 18:22.501
- Hey.
- My mom made brisket.

18:22.502 --> 18:23.680
Oh, thanks.

18:23.704 --> 18:25.682
So, uh, how's Virginia?

18:25.706 --> 18:27.017
She's recovering.

18:27.041 --> 18:28.604
Listen, I need your help with Dean.

18:28.628 --> 18:30.004
He is going through something,

18:30.028 --> 18:31.863
and I have no idea what he might do.

18:31.865 --> 18:34.088
Okay, well, I'm out of a job, Desna.

18:34.113 --> 18:36.692
- What's going on with the clinic?
- Okay, one thing at a time, Kenneth.

18:36.716 --> 18:38.894
Right now, I need you to go in the chapel

18:38.918 --> 18:41.163
and talk him through his feelings.

18:41.187 --> 18:43.966
But I'm just a dealer...
I mean, I'm a doctor.

18:43.990 --> 18:45.567
