18:45.591 --> 18:46.768
Okay, but your mama is.

18:46.792 --> 18:48.304
Some of that shit had to rub off.

18:48.328 --> 18:50.572
Besides, you want him
talking to a stranger

18:50.596 --> 18:51.773
about the shit that went down?

18:51.797 --> 18:52.996
I'm just a general practitioner.

18:52.998 --> 18:54.576
I know general medical things.

18:54.600 --> 18:56.178
He said he wanted to track down

18:56.202 --> 18:58.648
the person who shot Virginia
and hurt them.

18:58.672 --> 19:00.316
With what, his colored pencils?

19:00.340 --> 19:02.518
He needs help, Kenneth.

19:02.542 --> 19:05.120
I-I don't... I don't have
any specialized training

19:05.144 --> 19:07.611
except for the podiatry seminar
in the Keys.

19:07.613 --> 19:10.259
He's in the chapel. Go.

19:10.283 --> 19:12.328
Now.

19:12.352 --> 19:14.485
Okay, okay.

19:23.829 --> 19:27.191
So, Dean, how... how are your feet?

19:27.833 --> 19:29.211
Th-They're well, thank you.

19:29.235 --> 19:30.634
I-I-I wear gel insoles.

19:30.636 --> 19:32.837
Oh, me, too. Me, too. Mm.

19:35.841 --> 19:38.220
I hear you're feeling upset.

19:38.244 --> 19:40.690
I'm no longer suffering from any upset.

19:40.714 --> 19:43.292
My main focus now is to take action.

19:43.316 --> 19:45.427
I know my sister can't handle me
wanting to murder someone,

19:45.451 --> 19:49.699
but a black man has to take
action and fight the power.

19:49.723 --> 19:52.056
Well, you realize we're in Florida.

19:52.058 --> 19:53.235
Yeah.

19:53.259 --> 19:55.437
I will take a knee and a gun
for my beliefs.

19:55.461 --> 19:56.505
Yeah.

19:56.529 --> 19:57.773
Maybe it would be better

19:57.797 --> 20:00.576
if you focused your, um, negative emotion

20:00.600 --> 20:02.866
into something positive.

20:02.868 --> 20:04.646
What you really need is a new purpose,

20:04.670 --> 20:06.870
something to put your energy in.

20:06.872 --> 20:08.584
What could you do?

20:08.608 --> 20:10.709
Drawing. You're... You're good at that.

20:10.733 --> 20:12.677
Stripping?

20:14.014 --> 20:15.524
You're great at that.

20:15.549 --> 20:16.749
You do a few cherry pops,

20:16.774 --> 20:18.551
see if that doesn't calm you down.

20:18.576 --> 20:20.888
Cherry pops are not the answer, Dr. Ken.

20:21.220 --> 20:23.265
The only thing that will
give me satisfaction

20:23.289 --> 20:26.090
is hunting down the animals
that shot Virginia

20:26.092 --> 20:27.603
and blowing their heads off.

20:27.627 --> 20:31.073
I'm gonna a-assume that you're upset

20:31.097 --> 20:32.608
and, uh, prone to hyperbole.

20:32.632 --> 20:35.760
Dr. Ken, I killed before.
I'm very good at it.

20:36.282 --> 20:37.720
Very, very good.

20:38.704 --> 20:40.973
The sensation is oddly satisfying.

20:41.775 --> 20:43.619
I just don't want anyone

20:43.643 --> 20:48.424
to hurt anybody in my family ever again.

21:00.760 --> 21:02.472
Aww, this is from Bambi.

21:02.497 --> 21:04.407
- Peaches?
- Peaches!

21:04.730 --> 21:05.908
- Hi.
- Jenn!

21:05.932 --> 21:07.109
- Jenn?
- Oh, hi.

21:07.133 --> 21:08.391
- What are you doing here?
- Jennifer Husser,

21:08.415 --> 21:10.222
I told you to keep
your black ass in Tampa.

21:10.246 --> 21:13.190
Girl, you know I can't
stay away when I want to.

21:13.214 --> 21:14.784
Well, she's not up yet.

21:14.808 --> 21:17.186
Oh, God. Look at her.

21:17.210 --> 21:20.055
Not a single pore. How does she do it?

21:20.079 --> 21:22.591
It's easy, girl. Noxzema.

21:22.615 --> 21:24.118
Virginia! Virginia!

21:24.142 --> 21:25.483
Wait.

21:25.509 --> 21:27.287
Why can I only see out of one eye?

21:27.287 --> 21:28.598
Okay. It's okay.

21:28.622 --> 21:29.865
Am I missing an eye?

21:29.889 --> 21:31.066
Shh! No, no, no. No, no, no.

21:31.090 --> 21:33.535
The bullet just... it grazed you.

21:33.559 --> 21:35.070
- It's just a graze.
- Okay?

21:35.094 --> 21:37.473
A-A-And you had
to have a cornea transplant,

21:37.497 --> 21:38.874
but you are gonna be fine.

21:38.898 --> 21:40.054
A cornea transplant?

21:40.078 --> 21:41.740
Your other cornea is bullshit.

21:41.764 --> 21:43.636
Thank God, I saved my Bedazzler

21:43.661 --> 21:45.014
- from high school.
- Check this out.

21:45.038 --> 21:47.571
And we hooked your pretty little ass up.

21:47.573 --> 21:49.084
- Ooh, la la!
- Que lindo!

21:49.108 --> 21:51.621
And you're only gonna have to
wear it for a few days anyway.

21:51.645 --> 21:53.288
That's so beautiful. It's denim.

21:53.312 --> 21:55.272
You'll look as hot as ever,
like a sexual pirate.

21:55.274 --> 21:57.315
Virginia? Virginia.

22:00.386 --> 22:02.298
I-I-I was extremely anxious,

22:02.322 --> 22:04.966
but... but I-I checked out
your doctor on Yelp,

22:04.990 --> 22:06.726
a-and he has 4 1/2 stars.

22:07.834 --> 22:09.211
I-I'll be right back in a sec.

22:09.236 --> 22:10.346
- Just...
- Okay.

22:10.938 --> 22:12.796
Look what Polly made me.

22:12.798 --> 22:15.110
So, what's going on? How is he?

22:15.134 --> 22:18.180
Desna, your brother has
a serious revenge fantasy.

22:18.204 --> 22:19.581
You definitely have
to keep an eye on him.

22:19.605 --> 22:21.017
Encourage him to find a new focus.

22:21.017 --> 22:23.195
I've been keeping an eye on him
my whole life, Kenneth.

22:23.219 --> 22:24.396
That's not gonna change.

22:24.420 --> 22:26.732
Good, because I think
he's blurring his fantasy life

22:26.756 --> 22:27.771
with real life.

22:27.795 --> 22:29.081
Say what, now?

22:30.026 --> 22:32.460
He told me he killed someone.

22:33.029 --> 22:34.295
He said that?

22:35.254 --> 22:39.679
He's probably just
exhausted and dehydrated.

22:39.703 --> 22:43.015
Um, I'ma get him some kombucha.

22:43.039 --> 22:45.222
H-He'll be fine. Thanks.

22:48.517 --> 22:49.621
So?

22:49.645 --> 22:50.890
What happened with the girl

22:50.914 --> 22:52.291
that Mac and Melba tried to kill?

22:52.315 --> 22:53.493
Did you talk to her?

22:53.517 --> 22:54.827
Bitch pulled a "Lady Bird" on me.

22:54.851 --> 22:57.497
- She jumped out the car?
- Yeah, yeah.

22:57.521 --> 22:59.653
I'm surprised your ass saw that movie.

22:59.655 --> 23:01.901
- Well, only the first scene.
- Shit.

23:01.925 --> 23:04.370
Yo, I couldn't catch her, but
she left her purse in my car.

23:04.394 --> 23:05.771
Well, good. Did you go to her house?

23:05.795 --> 23:08.774
Yeah, old girl tried to shoot my ass.

23:08.798 --> 23:09.931
Shit.

23:11.535 --> 23:13.179
- Oh, hey.
- Hey.

23:13.203 --> 23:14.847
Um, why didn't you call me?

23:14.871 --> 23:16.516
I didn't know you got out.

23:16.540 --> 23:19.051
I got the Bat-Signal.
I had to see Virginia.

23:19.075 --> 23:20.720
I was gonna call you after.

23:20.744 --> 23:22.121
Well, you want to grab dinner?

23:22.145 --> 23:24.190
We can do Mexican... your favorite.

23:24.214 --> 23:26.258
Not with everything that's going on.

23:26.282 --> 23:28.883
Oh, we can, uh... we can
make it short. Entrées only.

23:28.885 --> 23:30.885
No guac before and no flan after.

23:30.887 --> 23:33.487
I'm just really worried about,
you know, Virginia's eye.

23:33.489 --> 23:36.602
Well Virginia's eye
doesn't care whether you...

23:36.626 --> 23:38.292
I'll talk to you later, okay?

23:38.294 --> 23:39.805
- Okay?
- You... You... You look...

23:39.829 --> 23:41.673
You look good, Polly.

23:41.697 --> 23:43.739
Plaid has never looked better.

23:56.312 --> 23:57.753
What's up?

23:58.047 --> 24:00.589
- I can feel something's wrong.
- I-I'm just worried

24:00.613 --> 24:03.429
that whoever hurt you I-is
gonna come back and kill us.

24:03.453 --> 24:06.432
They're not coming back.
Everything's gonna be alright.

24:06.456 --> 24:07.521
But... But you don't know that.

24:07.523 --> 24:09.235
I do.

24:09.259 --> 24:11.837
Everything happens for a reason, Dean.

24:11.861 --> 24:14.306
Maybe it's God or the Buddha

24:14.330 --> 24:16.709
or a big, beautiful queen in the sky

24:16.733 --> 24:19.024
with a poppin' weave named Tanika.

24:19.775 --> 24:23.571
Whoever it is, they have a plan.

24:23.940 --> 24:25.718
Everything that's ever happened...

24:25.742 --> 24:29.343
me getting shot, Joseline
leaving "Love & Hip Hop,"

24:29.345 --> 24:32.058
everyone wearing high-waisted jeans...

24:32.082 --> 24:35.165
is all a part of a divine order.

24:35.752 --> 24:37.663
There's something different about you.

24:37.687 --> 24:40.266
Mm. I do feel kinda funny.

24:40.290 --> 24:41.667
I-I-I think you're just suffering

24:41.691 --> 24:43.669
from the effects of the anesthesia.

24:43.693 --> 24:45.271
C-Can I get you something? Your phone?

24:45.295 --> 24:48.408
I bet a lot's happened
on... on Instagram and Snapchat.

24:48.432 --> 24:50.231
No, baby, I'm okay.

24:53.102 --> 24:56.270
Never felt better.

25:00.243 --> 25:01.421
May I help you?

25:01.445 --> 25:04.778
Yeah, uh, just wanted to return this.

25:04.780 --> 25:06.047
How'd you get this?

25:07.383 --> 25:08.382
Aw, hell, no.

25:08.384 --> 25:09.495
Wait.

25:09.519 --> 25:11.820
We know what Mac and Melba did to you.

25:13.056 --> 25:14.705
We wanna help.

25:19.729 --> 25:22.442
Why'd you catch that beatdown?

25:22.466 --> 25:23.998
And why should I trust you?

25:24.000 --> 25:26.178
I'm part owner of the casino now.

25:26.202 --> 25:28.047
We can protect you.

25:28.071 --> 25:29.915
No one can protect me from them.

25:29.939 --> 25:32.206
Y'all don't know Mac and Melba.

25:32.208 --> 25:34.433
Y'all in bed with the devil.

25:35.011 --> 25:39.413
Well, whenever they get finished
with what they need you for,

25:39.415 --> 25:42.328
you gonna end up
catching a bullet in your head.

25:42.352 --> 25:44.786
Yeah, them windows don't look
bulletproof to me.

25:50.360 --> 25:51.804
Okay.

25:51.828 --> 25:53.739
Why don't we just go to the police?

25:53.763 --> 25:55.607
I'll call my guy up.

25:55.631 --> 25:56.742
Okay, okay, okay! Okay, look.

25:56.766 --> 25:58.010
I'm the accountant

25:58.034 --> 25:59.945
for the biggest money launderer
in the state.

25:59.969 --> 26:01.347
I'm just as guilty as they are.

26:01.371 --> 26:04.750
They just got pissed because
I asked for a pay raise

26:04.774 --> 26:06.018
to keep doing their dirty business.

26:06.042 --> 26:07.286
Why didn't they kill you?

26:07.310 --> 26:09.093
Because they need me.

26:09.513 --> 26:10.945
What they don't know is...

26:14.650 --> 26:16.628
...I got this.

26:16.652 --> 26:18.097
Yes, bitch.

26:18.121 --> 26:21.055
And by the way, I cut that check for you.

26:21.057 --> 26:24.626
That 50 grand? Boo, you got robbed.

26:28.964 --> 26:31.377
The flash drive said
the casino is laundering

26:31.401 --> 26:33.067
$2 million a month.

26:33.069 --> 26:34.847
That sounds like killin' money to me.

26:34.871 --> 26:36.382
You think the casino freaks killed you?

26:36.406 --> 26:38.050
Maybe they want Ruval's cut?

26:38.074 --> 26:39.919
That didn't work out,
so they tried to buy you out.

26:39.943 --> 26:41.521
Virginia could have been killed.

26:41.545 --> 26:43.322
I am so sick of this shit.

26:43.346 --> 26:45.257
I'm tired of people
thinking they can play me

26:45.281 --> 26:47.059
and that I'm just gonna
roll over and take it.

26:47.083 --> 26:48.260
I'm done.

26:48.284 --> 26:50.863
I'm taking this casino,
and I'm protecting my girls.

26:50.887 --> 26:52.064
I don't know, D.

26:52.088 --> 26:53.665
I think you should listen to homegirl.

26:53.689 --> 26:55.735
I mean, they tortured her
for asking for a raise.

26:55.759 --> 26:57.002
Sure you want those kind of problems?

26:57.026 --> 26:59.872
The old Desna wouldn't have.

27:01.231 --> 27:02.674
But I'm a boss now.

27:02.698 --> 27:04.076
If you a boss,

27:04.100 --> 27:05.983
you should lock the front door.

27:07.103 --> 27:08.703
We gotta talk.

27:10.907 --> 27:12.948
I know who tried to take you out.

27:36.666 --> 27:38.199
Alright, bitch.

27:42.405 --> 27:44.338
Why would Clint want to kill me?

27:44.340 --> 27:46.252
He's pissed you didn't take the deal.

27:46.276 --> 27:47.920
Thought you disrespected our family.

27:47.944 --> 27:49.521
And you just now tellin' us?

27:49.545 --> 27:51.657
- 'Cause I just found out.
- Bullshit.

27:51.681 --> 27:53.147
Why would you give your boy up?

27:53.149 --> 27:55.261
I did it for you, Roller. That's why.

27:55.285 --> 27:58.264
I know it's been bad between us.
That's about to change.

27:58.288 --> 28:00.496
Clint's family, but so are you.

28:01.291 --> 28:03.058
Do what you want with that.

28:12.629 --> 28:14.629
_

28:16.413 --> 28:18.413
