- What do you want?!

28:56.212 --> 28:57.523
You don't even return my calls!

28:57.547 --> 28:58.991
Oh, we been through this shit
before, alright?

28:59.015 --> 29:00.526
I'm not doing it again!

29:00.550 --> 29:01.815
Yeah, we are.

29:01.817 --> 29:02.951
Bitch.

29:16.566 --> 29:18.133
Hey.

29:20.436 --> 29:21.613
Is Clint in there, huh?

29:21.637 --> 29:22.887
- No, he's not here.
- Huh?

29:22.911 --> 29:24.272
Is everything okay?

29:25.509 --> 29:27.583
No, everything's not okay.

29:28.578 --> 29:29.755
Found out it was Clint

29:29.779 --> 29:31.623
who tried to kill Desna, didn't you?

29:31.647 --> 29:33.625
Roller, Clint's gone crazy.

29:33.649 --> 29:35.027
Hey, Toby.

29:35.051 --> 29:36.228
It's gonna be alright.
Take a deep breath.

29:36.252 --> 29:39.031
No, it's not gonna be okay, Roller.

29:39.055 --> 29:42.097
He asked me to dump his motorcycle gear.

29:42.658 --> 29:44.570
That makes me an accessory.

29:44.594 --> 29:45.771
Listen to me.

29:45.795 --> 29:48.437
You see him, you hit me up, okay?

29:48.998 --> 29:51.465
I will if he doesn't kill me first.

29:51.467 --> 29:52.834
You'll be alright.

29:57.273 --> 29:59.441
I'm gonna need you
to get on the waxing train.

30:02.078 --> 30:03.535
What's going on?

30:04.013 --> 30:06.079
That was just a drive-by.

30:07.083 --> 30:09.061
Come again?

30:09.085 --> 30:11.251
Get in, get off, get out.

30:12.622 --> 30:14.171
You serious?

30:14.824 --> 30:17.325
- After all that?
- After all that.

30:20.163 --> 30:23.097
So, how's Tampa? Details.

30:23.099 --> 30:25.144
It's... beautiful.

30:25.168 --> 30:26.612
It's beautiful.

30:26.636 --> 30:29.281
I mean, it's... You know, it's
way better than Palmetto.

30:29.305 --> 30:30.939
Y'all happy out there, huh?

30:32.642 --> 30:34.108
It's... It's magical.

30:34.110 --> 30:35.354
Yeah, yeah.

30:35.378 --> 30:38.490
Ooh, y'all got, uh...
Queen B. there tonight.

30:38.514 --> 30:40.492
Abort, abort. That's sensitive right now.

